reproduce[source]

reproduce(down_path:"The directory where all the files will be downloaded and extracted to.", out_path:"The output path to place all results in.", vis_model:"The type of visual model. Can be either SimCLR or SIFT, taking ~6h or >24h, respectively, for all apps on our machine with 755G of RAM and 72 CPUs.")

Function for reproducing all results related to this tool's paper
